OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FITV Border political reporter Matty
OL,7,FSutton reflects on the race in
OL,8,FEttrick, Roxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,10,FEttrick, Roxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,11,Fcovers key Borders towns including
OL,12,FHawick, Jedburgh, Kelso, Duns and
OL,13,FEyemouth.
OL,15,FBut what are the different parties
OL,16,Fpromising if they win the seat?
OL,18,FScottish Conservatives
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
