PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FIn 2021 it was won by the Scottish
OL,7,FConservatives Rachael Hamilton. Her
OL,8,Fparty has held this seat since it was
OL,9,Fcreated in 2011. It is considered one
OL,10,Fof the safest Tory seats in Scotland.
OL,12,FNational polling, though, suggests her
OL,13,Fparty is on course to fall behind
OL,14,FLabour and Reform in opposition
OL,15,Ffollowing the vote on 7 May.
OL,17,FMs Hamilton, who is the deputy leader
OL,18,Fof her party, is standing on a promise
OL,19,Fto cut taxes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV Border, she
OL,7,Fdid not rule out holding ambitions for
OL,8,Fthe leadership after the election.
OL,10,FLeader Russell Findlay has said he
OL,11,Fwill not quit even if his party
OL,12,Fperforms poorly.
OL,14,FMs Hamilton said: "I'm sure Russell
OL,15,FFindlay will still be leader of the
OL,16,FScottish conservatives after the
OL,17,Felection. He's been a fantastic
OL,18,Fleader."
OL,26,@vD@SOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FAsked if she would want to be leader
OL,7,Fif Mr Findlay does step down, she
OL,8,Fsaid: "Well, we'll have to see what
OL,9,Fhappens after the election."
OL,11,FThe main challenger in Ettrick,
OL,12,FRoxburgh and Berwickshire is the SNP.
OL,13,FTheir candidate John Redpath says
OL,14,Fpeople in the area "feel forgotten."
OL,16,FHe said: "I'm a Borderer to my core
OL,17,Fand I think we have been forgotten
OL,18,Fabout down here by many
OL,19,Frepresentations. I know I've got the
OL,20,Fpassion and the skills to make a real
OL,21,Fchange here."
OL,26,@pD@GOUqD@\O]vD@TOUvD@dO]xD@JOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FSecuring independence for Scotland is
OL,7,Fa key priority of his party. At their
OL,8,Fconference last year, members voted to
OL,9,Fadopt leader John Swinney's plan to
OL,10,Fdemand a referendum if the SNP wins a
OL,11,Fmajority of seats at Holyrood in this
OL,12,Felection.
OL,14,FMr Redpath believes, however, that a
OL,15,Fmajority of independence-supporting
OL,16,FMSPs - so Scottish Green and SNP
OL,17,Fmembers combined - would be a mandate
OL,18,Ffor a second referendum.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FIn 2014 - 67% of people in the Borders
OL,7,Fvoted no to Scotland becoming an
OL,8,Findependent country.
OL,10,FMr Redpath said: "If the people vote
OL,11,Ffor parties that have a referendum in
OL,12,Fplace then a referendum should happen,
OL,13,Fit's a basic principle of democracy."
OL,15,FReform UK Scotland
OL,17,FJamie Langan, from Edinburgh, is
OL,18,Fstanding for Reform UK Scotland.
OL,26,@rD@ROUuD@eOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FHe said: "I freely admit I'm not local
OL,7,Fbut it's a part of the world I've
OL,8,Fspent a lot of time in and really
OL,9,Flove. It would be an absolute honour
OL,10,Fto represent it and a privilege to
OL,11,Fcall it home."
OL,13,FIn 2021 his party didn't stand a
OL,14,Fcandidate in this constituency. On the
OL,15,Flist they received less than 1% of the
OL,16,Fvote.
OL,18,FNational polling, however, suggests
OL,19,Fthey are now in a close battle with
OL,20,FLabour to be the main opposition in
OL,21,Fthe next Scottish Parliament.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FMr Langan says he backs their Scottish
OL,7,Fleader Malcolm Offord's stance that he
OL,8,Fis standing to become First Minister.
OL,10,FAt the party's campaign launch in
OL,11,FRenfrewshire two weeks ago, Reform UK
OL,12,Fleader Nigel Farage said the party was
OL,13,Faiming to be the "official opposition"
OL,14,Fat Holyrood.
OL,26,@uD@ROUuD@fO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FMr Langan said: "I believe Malcolm
OL,7,FOfford is running to be First
OL,8,FMinister. You have to remember we're
OL,9,Fcoming at this from a standing start,
OL,10,Fthis was a party at the last election
OL,11,Fthat got under a percent of the vote.
OL,12,FWe've made absolutely amazing strides
OL,13,Fforward, we've got all the momentum at
OL,14,Fthe moment, we'll see where it takes
OL,15,Fus."
OL,17,FScottish Labour
OL,26,@nD@QOUwD@DO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/22
