OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FAt the 2024 General Election, in which
OL,7,FLabour won a landslide, their party's
OL,8,Fcandidate for the Borders increased
OL,9,Fher vote share, overtaking the Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats to come third.
OL,12,FSince then, polls suggest support for
OL,13,Fthe party in Scotland has fallen as a
OL,14,Fresult of unpopular UK Government
OL,15,Fpolicies.
OL,17,FKaymarie Hughes is the Scottish Labour
OL,18,Fcandidate for this constituency. She
OL,19,Fbacked leader Anas Sarwar's call for
OL,20,Fthe Prime Minister to resign.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FMs Hughes is also Unison Scotland's
OL,7,FLGBT+convenor and a strong supporter
OL,8,Fof trans rights.
OL,10,FShe said: "I think everybody has the
OL,11,Fright to live how they want to live.
OL,12,FI'm not frightened about a trans
OL,13,Fperson sharing a bathroom with me. I
OL,14,Fdo understand the idea of safe spaces
OL,15,Ffor women and I think we need to bring
OL,16,Fboth parties together and get a happy
OL,17,Fmedium for everybody."
OL,26,@rD@KOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FScottish Labour has changed its
OL,7,Fposition on gender self-
OL,8,Fidentification. In 2023 the party
OL,9,Fbacked the Gender Recognition Reform
OL,10,FBill which would have allowed trans
OL,11,Fpeople to change gender without
OL,12,Fmedical sign-off.
OL,14,FMr Sarwar reversed that position over
OL,15,Fconcerns about the impact on single
OL,16,Fsex spaces such as toilets and prisons.
OL,18,FAsked whether she was disappointed by
OL,19,Fthe u-turn, Ms Hughes said: "I'm
OL,20,Falways disappointed when LGBT issues
OL,21,Faren't front and foremost."
OL,26,@{D@]OU}D@[O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FScottish Liberal Democrats
OL,8,FThe Liberal Democrats have failed to
OL,9,Fget a foothold here since the
OL,10,Fconstituency was created in 2011.
OL,11,FAfter topping the polls here in the
OL,12,Fearly years of devolution, their
OL,13,Fpopularity has since dwindled.
OL,15,FThe 2010 Conservative and Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrat UK Government coalition,
OL,17,Fbrokered by David Cameron and Nick
OL,18,FClegg, saw their support contract in
OL,19,FScotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FRay Georgeson, Scottish Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat candidate for Ettrick,
OL,8,FRoxburgh and Berwickshire, said the
OL,9,Fcoalition had been a "hard lesson" for
OL,10,Fhis party, but they had "learnt it."
OL,12,FAsked about leader Alex Cole-
OL,13,FHamilton's pledge to support the
OL,14,FLabour party if no party wins an
OL,15,Foutright majority after the election,
OL,16,FMr Georgeson said: "We'll dust off and
OL,17,Fput the bruises to one side now and
OL,18,Ftry again."
OL,20,FFull list of candidates standing in
OL,21,FEttrick, Roxburgh and Berwickshire
