OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FJohn Redpath, Scottish National Party
OL,7,F(SNP)
OL,9,FKey issues for voters in Ettrick,
OL,10,FRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,12,FLocal businesses have warned trading
OL,13,Fis "tough" as a result of rising
OL,14,Fprices and ongoing economic
OL,15,Funcertainty.
OL,17,FSmall businesses are often described
OL,18,Fas the 'backbone' of the Scottish
OL,19,FBorders economy.
OL,26,@uD@DOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FIain Campbell, who runs Campbell
OL,7,FButchers in Hawick said: "It's been
OL,8,Ftough. You're constantly battling,
OL,9,Fyou're constantly looking at your
OL,10,Fprices."
OL,12,FHe gave the example of one supplier
OL,13,Fwhich he said had raised its prices by
OL,14,F42% in the last five years.
OL,16,FGraeme Webb, has a photography studio
OL,17,Fon Hawick high street.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FHe said: "Covid obviously was a big
OL,7,Ffactor and then after that the cost of
OL,8,Feverything seemed to rocket. Paper for
OL,9,Fme, as a photographer went through the
OL,10,Froof, as did electricity with the
OL,11,FUkraine war and then we've just had a
OL,12,Flot of uncertainty and recently again
OL,13,Fprices have gone up so it's been very
OL,14,Fchallenging."
OL,16,FA charity which teaches people to grow
OL,17,Ftheir own food told ITV Border that
OL,18,Ffood security and social isolation are
OL,19,Fkey issues.
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G18/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FAbundant Borders has eight community
OL,7,Fgardens across the Scottish Borders.
OL,9,FThe constituency is rural and many
OL,10,Fpeople live in remote areas.
OL,12,FPete Saunders, operations manager at
OL,13,FAbundant Borders, said: "The two main
OL,14,Fthings we're looking at doing is
OL,15,Fincreasing food security and
OL,16,Fdecreasing social isolation. Because
OL,17,Fwe're in such a wide rural area these
OL,18,Flittle hubs can bring people together."
OL,26,@uD@YOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G19/22
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775481061
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders - Ettrick,
OL,4,CRoxburgh and Berwickshire
OL,6,FKirsten Bowers, who volunteers in
OL,7,FKelso, said the garden had helped her
OL,8,Fovercome her struggle with
OL,9,Fagoraphobia, a condition which had
OL,10,Fmade it difficult for her to leave her
OL,11,Fhouse.
OL,13,FCarys Dawes, who runs the Kelso
OL,14,Fgarden, added: "The garden is partly
OL,15,Fabout the garden but mostly about the
OL,16,Fpeople and just watching people like
OL,17,FKirsten grow is amazing."
OL,19,F2021 RESULTS: Ettrick, Roxburgh and
OL,20,FBerwickshire
